<div class="process-box">
    <div class="process-title-box">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
                <h6 class="process-word">기본 정보</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
                <h6 class="process-word-highlighted">수업 계획서</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
                <h6 class="process-word">경력 증명</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
                <h6 class="process-word">스웨터 요청완료</h6>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="percentage-bar">
        <div class="progress-bar-b">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-box">
        <div class="profile-top-box">
            <p class="text-center" style="color:#ffffff">가장 잘 할 수 있는 강의를 개설해 주세요! 스웨티들이 배우고 싶은 마음이 생길 수 있도록 작성해 주시면 좋아요!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-box-container">
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="span-area">
                    <span>스웨팅 썸네일</span>
                </div>
                <div class="thumbnailsec">
                    <div class="imgcon">
                            <input type="file" class="imageup" id="imgattach" onchange="LoadImg(this)" accept="image/*">
                            <img class="uploadimg" id="LoadImg" src="" alt="">
                        </div>
                    <div class="radiocon">
                        <label for="auto" class="auto" id="autolabel">
                            <input type="radio" id="auto" class="thumbradio" name="thumbnail" class="form-control thumbnail"
                               onclick="changecolor()" value="프로필">thumbnail 프로필(자동생성)</label>
                        <label for="direct" class="direct" id="directlabel" style="color :#394DD1">
                            <input type="radio" id="direct" class="thumbradio" name="thumbnail" checked="checked"
                                class="form-control thumbnail" onclick="changecolor()" value="이미지">thumbnail 이미지(직접입력)</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="span-area">
                    <span>스웨팅 제목</span>
                </div>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="예)react기초">
            </div>
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="span-area">
                    <span>스웨팅 내용</span>
                </div>
                <textarea class="form-control" style="resize: none;" rows="3"
                    placeholder="수업을 어떻게 진행하실 건지 자유롭게 적어주세요. 예)react기초에 대해 공부합니다"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="span-area">
                    <span>스웨팅 언어(중복선택 불가)</span>
                </div>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="예)Python">
            </div>
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="span-area">
                    <span>수업 비용(시간당 비용을 입력해주세요)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="costcon">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control costleft">~
                    <input type="text" class="form-control costright">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="span-area">
                    <span>추천 대상</span>
                </div>
                <select name="" id="" class=" recommendsel">
                    <option value="">어떤 분에게 강의를 추천하고 싶나요?</option>
                    <option value=""></option>
                    <option value=""></option>
                    <option value=""></option>
                    <option value=""></option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column-agree">
            <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="defaultCheck1" style="margin-top:8px;">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="defaultCheck1">
                    위 내용은 타인의 저작권을 침해하지 않음을 확인합니다. 저작권관련 권리침해신고가 접수되는 경우 게시중단 될 수 있습니다.
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="defaultCheck1" style="margin-top:8px;">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="defaultCheck1">
                    스웨터 등록이 완료되면, 추가 수업 계획서를 작성하실 수 있습니다.
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="button-box-area">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <button>취소</button>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <button>저장</button>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <button>다음</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>